, "value": "Translation of Le pur et l'impur."}, "number_of_pages": 172, "languages": [{"key": "/languages/eng"}], "lccn": ["68143850"], "isbn_10": ["0436105179"], "publish_date": "1968", "publish_country": "enk", "by_statement": "[by] Colette; translated from the French by Herma Briffault, introduction by Janet Flanner.", "work_title": ["Pur et l'impur."], "works": [{"key": "/works/OL1184845W"}], "type": {"key": "/type/edition"}, "local_id": ["urn:bwbsku:KP-324-267"], "covers": [13571444], "latest_revision": 7, "revision": 7, "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2008-04-01T03:28:50.625462"}, "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2023-03-17T17:58:12.130936"}}, {"publishers": ["New York Review of Books"], "number_of_pages": 184, "isbn_10": ["094032248X"], "covers": [717564], "lc_classifications": ["PQ2605.O28 P813 2000", "PQ2605.O28P813 2000", "PQ2605.O28 P8+"], "key": "/books/OL6776424M", "authors": [{"key": "/authors/OL119715A"}], "ocaid": "pureimpure0000cole", "publish_places": ["New York"], "contributions": ["Briffault, Herma."], "work_title": ["Pur et l'impur."], "pagination": "xviii, 184 p. ;", "source_records": ["marc:marc_openlibraries_sanfranciscopubliclibrary/sfpl_chq_2018_12_24_run02.mrc:59598750:2416", "ia:pureimpure0000cole", "marc:marc_loc_2016/BooksAll.2016.part01.utf8:2904514:771", "bwb:9780940322486", "marc:marc_columbia/Columbia-extract-20221130-006.mrc:231416034:1591"], "title": "The pure and the impure", "dewey_decimal_class": ["843/.912"], "identifiers": {"librarything": ["8193561"], "goodreads": ["89848"]}, "languages": [{"key": "/languages/eng"}], "lccn": ["00009532"], "local_id": ["urn:sfpl:31223019971325", "urn:sfpl:31223901658006", "urn:sfpl:31223077370048", "urn:sfpl:31223123600547"], "publish_date": "2000", "publish_country": "nyu", "by_statement": "Colette ; translated by Herma Briffault ; introduction by Judith Thurman.", "oclc_numbers": ["44083910"], "works": [{"key": "/works/OL1184845W"}], "type": {"key": "/type/edition"}, "description": {"type": "/type/text", "value": "\"This guided tour of the erotic nether-world with which Colette was so intimately acquainted begins in the darkness and languor of a fashionable opium den, and continues as a series of unforgettable encounters with men and, especially, women whose lives have been improbably and yet permanently transfigured by the power of desire.\n\nLucid and lyrical, The Pure and the Impure stands out as one of modern literature's subtlest reckonings not only with the varieties of sexual experience, but with the unlikely nature of love.\"--BOOK JACKET."}, "latest_revision": 11, "revision": 11, "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2008-04-01T03:28:50.625462"}, "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2024-07-12T22:11:31.054811"}}, {"publishers": ["Farrar, Straus & Giroux"], "identifiers": {"librarything": ["85824"]}, "lc_classifications": ["PQ2605.O28 C46 1967"], "key": "/books/OL5544252M", "authors": [{"key": "/authors/OL119715A"}], "publish_places": ["New York"], "pagination": "174 p.", "source_records": ["marc:marc_loc_2016/BooksAll.2016.part06.utf8:96371929:597", "marc:marc_columbia/Columbia-extract-20221130-004.mrc:204758481:1079", "marc:harvard_bibliographic_metadata/ab.bib.01.20150123.full.mrc:253727753:914", "ia:pureimpure0000cole_x7b1", "marc:harvard_bibliographic_metadata/20220215_020.bib.mrc:283348471:2580"], "title": "The pure and the impure.", "dewey_decimal_class": ["848/.9/1203"], "notes": {"type": "/type/text", "value": "Translation of Le pur et l'impur."}, "number_of_pages": 174, "languages": [{"key": "/languages/eng"}, {"key": "/languages/und"}], "lccn": ["67022433"], "publish_date": "1967", "publish_country": "nyu", "by_statement": "Translated by Herma Briffault. With an introd. by Janet Flanner.", "work_title": ["Pur et l'impur."], "works": [{"key": "/works/OL1184845W"}], "type": {"key": "/type/edition"}, "oclc_numbers": ["1167928"], "covers": [15046696], "ocaid": "pureimpure0000cole_x7b1", "description": {"type": "/type/text", "value": "It was Colette's desire to add to the limited treasury of truthful insights into love, into the mysteries of love in its many forms. She used her customery semifictional formula to report on the behavior, the mores, reflexes, instincts of women, especially as sentient, desiring creatures drawn to similarities and even to substitutes."}, "latest_revision": 8, "revision": 8, "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2008-04-01T03:28:50.625462"}, "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2025-11-03T06:53:33.194616"}}, {"publishers": ["Farrar & Rinehart, inc."], "identifiers": {"librarything": ["85824"]}, "subtitle": "a case-book of love", "lc_classifications": ["PQ2605.O28 C46 1933"], "latest_revision": 4, "key": "/books/OL6340547M", "authors": [{"key": "/authors/OL119715A"}], "publish_places": ["New York"], "contributions": ["Dally, Edith, tr."], "pagination": " xv, 229 p.", "source_records": ["marc:marc_loc_2016/BooksAll.2016.part03.utf8:135902808:627"], "title": "The pure and the impure", "lccn": ["36018699"], "number_of_pages": 229, "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2008-04-01T03:28:50.625462"}, "languages": [{"key": "/languages/eng"}], "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2020-09-15T10:00:43.000061"}, "publish_date": "1933", "publish_country": "nyu", "by_statement": "by Colette. Translated from the French by Edith Dally ; introduction by Joseph Collins.", "oclc_numbers": ["2454744"], "works": [{"key": "/works/OL1184845W"}], "type": {"key": "/type/edition"}, "revision": 4}, {"publishers": ["Adelphi"], "number_of_pages": 133, "classifications": {}, "contributors": [{"role": "Translator", "name": "Adriana Motti"}], "title": "Il puro e l'impuro", "identifiers": {}, "covers": [7104141], "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2012-04-19T11:48:46.157065"}, "physical_format": "Paperback", "isbn_10": ["8845912450"], "publish_date": "1996", "key": "/books/OL25285724M", "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2012-04-19T12:53:57.635819"}, "latest_revision": 3, "works": [{"key": "/works/OL1184845W"}], "type": {"key": "/type/edition"}, "revision": 3}]}